---
// Problem Section — The phosphorus crisis (investor urgency)
---

<section id="problem" class="relative overflow-hidden bg-dark-green text-white">
  <!-- Subtle background pattern -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03]" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 1px 1px, white 1px, transparent 0); background-size: 40px 40px;"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10">
    <!-- Opening statement -->
    <div class="container-custom py-20 md:py-28">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-16 reveal">
        <div class="inline-block mb-5 px-4 py-2 bg-white/10 rounded-full">
          <span class="text-white/80 font-semibold text-sm tracking-wide">THE OPPORTUNITY</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-display font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
          The world has a <br class="hidden md:block" />
          <span class="text-cream">phosphorus problem</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/60 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          A critical nutrient is being wasted on a massive scale — creating both an environmental crisis and a market opportunity.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Stats grid -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 lg:gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Stat 1 -->
        <div class="reveal stagger-1 group bg-white/[0.04] backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:bg-white/[0.08] transition-all duration-500">
          <div class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-display font-bold text-cream mb-3">80%</div>
          <div class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">of soil phosphorus is locked away</div>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Most phosphorus in agricultural soils is bound in organic and mineral forms that plants cannot access — decades of fertilizer application sitting unused underground.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Stat 2 -->
        <div class="reveal stagger-2 group bg-white/[0.04] backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:bg-white/[0.08] transition-all duration-500">
          <div class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-display font-bold text-cream mb-3">$70B+</div>
          <div class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">spent annually on phosphate fertilizers</div>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            The global phosphate fertilizer market continues to grow, yet efficiency remains stubbornly low — most applied phosphorus never reaches the plant.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Stat 3 -->
        <div class="reveal stagger-3 group bg-white/[0.04] backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:bg-white/[0.08] transition-all duration-500">
          <div class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-display font-bold text-cream mb-3">50–100</div>
          <div class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">years until global P reserves are depleted</div>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            At projected demand growth, accessible phosphate rock reserves could be exhausted within a century. Soil erosion is accelerating the crisis — stripping phosphorus faster than it can be replenished.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Stat 4 -->
        <div class="reveal stagger-4 group bg-white/[0.04] backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:bg-white/[0.08] transition-all duration-500">
          <div class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-display font-bold text-cream mb-3">#1</div>
          <div class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">cause of freshwater eutrophication</div>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Phosphorus runoff from agriculture is the primary driver of algal blooms, dead zones, and water quality degradation worldwide.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Transition statement -->
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mt-16 reveal">
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
          The phosphorus is already in the soil. <br class="hidden md:block" />
          <span class="text-white font-semibold">The challenge is unlocking it.</span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Sources -->
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-10 pt-6 border-t border-white/10">
        <p class="text-[10px] text-white/25 leading-relaxed text-center">
          Sources: USGS Mineral Commodity Summaries (2024) · Cordell et al., "Peak Phosphorus," <em>Sustainability</em> (2011) · Alewell et al., "Global phosphorus shortage will be aggravated by soil erosion," <em>Nature Communications</em> (2020) · Carpenter, "Eutrophication of aquatic ecosystems," <em>PNAS</em> (2005) · FAO World Fertilizer Trends and Outlook · Sattari et al., "Residual soil phosphorus," <em>PNAS</em> (2012)
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
